# Financial tests

- Assert against **tolerances** in rupees only when the spec allows (e.g. §10 EMI within ₹1).
- Prefer **table-driven tests** for amortisation months and PF tranche months (§7.3 off-by-one).
- When adding goldens, pin **rounding policy** and document in `README.md`.
